  <preparation>Whisk the sauce ingredients and use immediately or cover and refrigerate for up to a day.  Skewer shrimp and oil, salt and pepper to taste.  Grill shrimp normally and serve with the sauce.  Webber's: "ooo-wee".</preparation>
